data.description: It's a rare 2 story within a gated community!   Excellent location one block from Navigation BLVD.   Downstairs has one bedroom with its own bathroom and tile floors.  Upstairs has an open floor plan with a kitchen that is open to living area.  Kitchen has granite countertops.  Living room has wood laminate flooring. A HALF BATHROOM is located in upstairs for guest.    Master bathroom has large tub shower combination, tile floors, walk in closet and granite counter tops. Excellent side fenced yard!
